The paper deals with a learning algorithm for an online linear classification problem with strategic agents, which involves game theory, machine learning, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
